<TEXT>
<P>
Many Chinese people marked National Day by studying the report
of the 15th National Congress of the Communist Party of China.
</P>
<P>
In Jinan, capital of east China's Shandong province, officers
of the People's Liberation Army of the Jian Military Area Command
and officials of the provincial and municipal government held a
