<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, October 2 (Xinhua) -- The Hong Kong Airport
Authority today awarded a contract for providing 8,000 baggage
trolleys to be used in the new airport's passenger terminal,
according to a press release circulated here.
</P>
