system to lend money to the exporters of those crops on the basis
of receipts showing their transaction in specified warehouses.
</P>
<P>
Uganda now has commercial attaches in Kenya and Tanzania and
the government will appoint more attaches in foreign missions to
promote export, revealed the state minister. 
