On the downside, OUE was the biggest loser as it declined by 45
cents to end at 5.45 Singapore dollars. The United Overseas Bank
(UOB) Foreign fell by 40 cents to finish at 10.5 Singapore
dollars. Elec and Sea View closed 30 cents lower at 8.35 US
dollars and 9.2 Singapore dollars respectively.  
</P>
