<P>
The mishap occurred when the bus lost balance while crossing
the swollen rivulet, police said.
</P>
<P>
Though some passengers were believed to have managed to swim to
safety, the exact number could not be immediately ascertained,
police added.
</P>
<P>
The accident came on the heel of a similar mishap in the state
last week in which 43 passengers died when a bus plunged into a
river after hitting the railing of a bridge. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
