<HEADLINE> Rusedski Blasts into Second Round </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZURICH, October 1 (Xinhua) -- Big-serving players Greg Rusedski
and Mark Philippoussis blasted their way into the second round of
the Swiss indoor championships played in Basel on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Rusedski, the fourth seed and world number 10, collected his
12th win in 15 matches after coming back from a set down to record
a 4-6, 6-4, 7-5 victory over German David Prinosil.
</P>
